thread.title: Jimmy Ryan

author: Jimmy Ryan
title: Jimmy Ryan
text: after reviewing dozens of websites for an engagement ring, i found the perfect one here, it was custom made and i was very happy with the finished product, it was shipped overnight by fedex and i received it on christmas eve and surprised my now fiance, i purchased the led ring box and it set the diamond off with a beautiful sparkle. i would purchase from them again.
